{"tid":972094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超級血狼月現身 猶預警：有強國將垮台","createTime":"2019-01-07T07:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T07:43:16.000Z","uid":225846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0d602f82b1d225feb9c760eeb3f877b053cf87e5","tid":972094,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n在美東時間1月21日凌晨12點12分，天空上演難得一見的天文奇景，結合「超級月亮」、「血月」和「狼月」三大特色的天文奇觀「超級血狼月」（Super Blood Wolf Moon）。不過有猶太教拉比（rabbi，指猶太教律法專家或偉大的人）表示，「超級血狼月」出現，將預告著世界將會發生大事，例如有強大國家將垮台。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/O1hLTcW56xIBWqzsAZKXvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4xNTY4NjI3NDUwOTgwNw--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/i00VlFUxRD2o.r6RsNiyCA--~B/aD0yODc7dz01MTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/setn_com_683/1c4315a3b8cce77c2d7ef9b48c29829d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FO1hLTcW56xIBWqzsAZKXvA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4xNTY4NjI3NDUwOTgwNw--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fi00VlFUxRD2o.r6RsNiyCA--~B%2FaD0yODc7dz01MTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn_com_683%2F1c4315a3b8cce77c2d7ef9b48c29829d&h=665205e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲（圖／翻攝自pixabay）<br />\n<br />\n據以色列突發新聞（Breaking Israel News）報導，21日的「超級血狼月」當天，剛好是在猶太習俗中4個傳統新年之一的「猶太植樹節」（Tu B&rsquo;shva），也就是希伯來曆細罷特月（Shevat）的第15天，而此月亮徵兆，意味著「萬物的結局近了」。<br />\n<br />\n曾出書探討月蝕在猶太教中所代表的意義，猶太教的傑出拉比（rabbi）格納特（Mordechai Genut）提出警示表示，在細罷特月出現月蝕，即代表著世界的災難將會急速加快，像是地震和火山爆發會明顯增加，甚至比去年還多。並說，月蝕是太陽和月亮為了支配天空所產生的衝突現象，也代表地表上也會有類似的衝突，例如有些看起來很強大的國家控將垮台、有些看似弱小國家則會興盛起來。 <br />\n<br />\n據美國國家航空航天局（NASA）資料顯示，「超級血狼月」將1月21日凌晨12點12分登場，不過只限於只有北美、南美地區，以及歐洲西部和非洲部份地區看得到，因亞洲、澳洲、印度和靠近亞洲的多數太平洋島嶼，這時段為白天。（編輯：陳昱哲）"},{"pid":"c4609c505f0a2cab2ad30fd8890b9670df279627","tid":972094,"uid":94591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"月光有月經 一定有妖精"},{"pid":"28a2012e584b76e1079f8e5cbff5be7fe99b8c81","tid":972094,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:05:53.000Z","msg":"無限月讀"},{"pid":"769204a07f8399b52a736c8bcf5717aefc188ad7","tid":972094,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"美國 俄國<br />\n邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90550d87b8a606f49c91caede35350a66cef5720","tid":972094,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"769204a07f8399b52a736c8bcf5717aefc188ad7","tid":972094,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"美國 俄國<br />\n邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:07:40.000Z","msg":"好明顯中国啦"},{"pid":"1446c4ffa1297f4028b829b765a3de932342eb80","tid":972094,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:08:20.000Z","msg":"強國<br />\n強國<br />\n強國<br />\n強國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7db5ec592a5d88ec157b3473be5b93fca4a8ab9","tid":972094,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:23:44.000Z","msg":"支持中国倒台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a142a759fac92a0c41ac9edebad51e472bd07bb","tid":972094,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:25:43.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca9ce439403e4654f39312d8f45e63c7e47df29","tid":972094,"uid":44199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"支"}]}